::DrillBit::

DrillBit sees the others run to there positions. He decides to stay, and
help Stingtra, Terrorsaur, and KitKat.
"I dont know who you are, but I'm going to turn you in to scrap!" He
says to Adrax, shooting his gattaling gun some more.

::Hot Rod::

Hot Rod figures that the onw with the cloak is the most dangerous, so he
looks for the fringe effect. He spots it, although it was hard to keep
track of. He fires his two shoulder rockets at Double Punch.
